The Accomplice Chardonnay, De Bortoli, South Australia, 2021 

Grape variety, 100% Chardonnay   

This dry white wine from South Australia has lifted aromas of peach and nectarine complemented with some very subtle vanilla oak. A soft and creamy texture is balanced by fine acidity to give a clean and very long finish.   

Serve chilled and enjoy with fish and prawn pie, risotto, or a creamy chicken pasta.
